{"title":"EVOC Commute A.I.R. Pro Pack is a backpack airbag for cyclists","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/09/06/evoc-commute-a-i-r-pro-pack-for-cyclists-rapidly-inflates-in-a-crash/","date":1630930734000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-270396\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>EVOC have partnered with Minerva Air Bag Systems to produce a commuter pack for cyclists that rapidly inflates a hidden air bag in the event of a crash. This kind of technology isn’t new; we’ve seen it adapted for use by motorcyclists and construction workers who are regularly at risk of falling from height. Now, EVOC have reworked the technology, stuffing it discreetly away into an 18 Litre Back Pack for the cycle commuter; we got the low-down on the EVOC Commute A.I.R. Pro Pack, still a concept, at IAA Mobility.</p><h2>EVOC Commute A.I.R. Pro Pack</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists.jpg\" alt=\"evoc commuter air pro pack non-inflated\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072245/evoc-commuter-airbag-rapid-inflation-crash-protection-for-cyclists-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>EVOC have just massively upped their game with a next-level safety feature for the cycle commuter; the Airbag Integrated Rescue System. At a glance, the EVO Commute A.I.R. PRO 18 looks much like any other professional commuter pack, but tucked away inside is a bag that will automatically and rapidly inflate, expanding to cover the wearer’s neck, collar bones, chest and shoulders, during a crash.</p><p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/C2jqvDtRHsQ?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\"></iframe></p><p>The idea is that the bag inflates <em>before</em> you suffer an impact, inflating as you’re on the way to the ground. Multiple sensors are used to control activation of the bag, comparing the position of the rider’s body with the speed of motion. Full inflation occurs just 0.2 seconds following activation, and the bag remain inflated, protecting the wearer, for a further 5-10 seconds thereafter.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech.jpg\" alt=\"DUMMY COMMUTER FALLS BIKE CRASH WEARING EVOC COMMUTE A.I.R. PRO PACK INFLATES IMPACT\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072221/crash-simulation-evo-airbag-commuter-pack-safety-tech-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>So, it’s mainly going to work if you both decelerate suddenly <em>and</em> start to lift or roll dramatically. Scenarios i’m imaging include putting your front wheel in a pothole or tram track and getting sent over the bars, hitting a vehicle, or a car door that’s been thrown open without a moment’s thought.</p><div id=\"attachment_270650\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-270650\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator.jpg\" alt=\"evoc commute air pro pack chest clip activator\" width=\"1400\" height=\"523\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-800x299.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-120x45.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-768x287.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-800x299.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-120x45.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072241/evoc-commuter-airbag-pack-arming-light-indicator-768x287.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-270650\">You might want to unclip the chest strap to deactivate the system before you bend over to tie your shoelace or pick something up off the floor</p></div><p>The pack’s chest clip is an electrified Fidlock buckle that snaps closed using a magnet. It turns the system on and an indicator light tells you the status; red is arming, flashing green means it is ready to go and flashing red/green alternately means there’s a system error.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill.jpg\" alt=\"evoc commute air pro pack gas canister inflator\" width=\"1400\" height=\"1050\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1400px) 100vw, 1400px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill.jpg 1400w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072230/evoc-airbag-commuter-pack-gas-canister-refill-768x576.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>This is not a single-use safety feature. Inflation is delivered by the release of CO2 from a canister that is tucked away inside the lining of the pack. You can send the canister back to EVOC for a refill for $40 USD.&nbsp; The Airbag simply folds back up into the pack to be reused.</p><div id=\"attachment_270659\"><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-270659\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region.jpg\" alt=\"evoc commute airbag explode region\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06080632/evoc-commute-airbag-pack-white-zipper-release-region-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p id=\"caption-attachment-270659\">The Airbag bursts out from this white zippered region behind the wearer’s head. It is never actually closed, allowing the inflating bag to push open the rest of the zipper as it expands</p></div><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection.jpg\" alt=\"evoc commute airbag pack inflated rear view\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/06072249/evoc-inflating-commuter-pack-air-bag-crash-protection-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>Like many EVOC packs for winter sports and mountain biking, the Commute A.I.R. Pro also gets an integrated <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/06/23/evoc-back-protection-levels-up-w-new-evoc-liteshield-plus-protector-for-mtb-snow/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Liteshield Plus</a> Back Protector that runs the length of the pack. There’s also a wide and adjustable AIRO FLEX hip belt. Inside there’s a separate laptop compartment that can be accessed quickly by opening the side of the pack, as well as more organizer compartments for a phone, glasses and documents.</p><p>Three versions of the EVOC Commute will be available; a regular one without back protections, one with the Liteshield Plus, and then the top-end EVOC Commute A.I.R. Pro. None are likely to be available until 2023, and price for the latter is likely to be in the region of $800 USD, with refills available from $40 USD.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.evocusa.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>EVOCUSA.com</em></a></p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"4129ddf55aad2cb207369ff0ed5f1d21d73cff01801d5859f7f5eb3dfa4169ef","category":"Cycling"}